Map Maker = Spazztic_Killer
Maker Name = Bunker_Wars

First off this is my first map I have ever made and would like some feedback on it if you guys could.
If you find something wrong with it or you think it needs something to make it better please tell me and 
ill try my best to do it.
  
All the metal doors and windows open and close

To load map please copy all of these files into the file dir 
"C:\Program Files\Steam\steamapps\Account_Name\counter-strike source\cstrike\maps\" Or where ever you 
installed the game at.

I dont now weather or not you'll need the file named Bunker_Wars.ztmp I dont now what it is I think
it was made after I run the buildcubemaps commands but please copy that file also just in case.


If you want to leave me feedback please either leave it on this website that you downloaded this map
at www.fpsbanana.com or email me spazztic_killer@embarqmail.com

Thank You Spazztic_Killer
